column1: Maori Ethnic Group Estimated Resident Population by Age and Sex (1991+) (Annual-Jun)
All population estimates at 30 June 2018 and beyond use the 2018-base ERP.
Estimates flagged as provisional are subject to revision, mainly to incorporate revisions to external (international) migration estimates.
To produce a coherent annual national series, Maori population estimates from 1991 to 2018 do not incorporate results from the 1996 or 2013 Census.
Estimates are as at June year
